		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's been quite a while since i have programmed.  i've made the code for the states as data.  It doesn't work right.  The little ship flashes around a little and then vanishes.
<br />
<br />i remember debugging using a variable "look" located on the zero page close to $0000.  I would place "sta look" after a crucial line of code and then run nintendulator, pause it and see what value look contained.  
<br />
<br />Now, i cant figure out how that works with debugging.  How do you know when to pause nintendulator?  i have forgotten how to debug.  Could you please help refresh my memory a little?  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

