	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You set a watch on writes to 'look'. How to find where 'look' has been placed in RAM depends on your assembler (see if it can output a "symbol table"); how to set the watch depends on your emulator.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
