		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />How do you set a watch in nintendulaor?  i know that look is in spot #0006 because it's the 7th variable in the zero page variable list.  i can check its value in nintendulators disassembly screen.  Is that a watch?  (i've never heard of doing a watch before.)

		

