	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Nintendulator does not support "watches" (memory I/O breakpoints), only address execution breakpoints. If you want to watch for a memory write, you'll have to use a different emulator for that.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


